data.description: $5,000 CREDIT towards the Buyer's closing cost!. Discover a Golf Lover's Haven in The Woodburn Estates & Golf: a vibrant 55+ Active Community. Embrace mornings on your covered patio, sipping coffee while gazing at the 2nd hole of the Golf Course. This 2-bed, 1-bath gem boasts a fireplace with a pellet insert, an updated open kitchen with modern appliances, ceiling fans, wood parquet flooring in the entry, dining & kitchen, and hardwoods in bedrooms. Enjoy a bonus office space, one-year-old roof, newer furnace/AC, inside utilities, pantry, and an oversized one-car garage. Your peaceful retreat awaits.
